# menu_focus_grapher_smoke.numos — Phase 9C Main Menu focused-card visual candidate.
#
# Phase 9B proved the launcher arrows move the LOGICAL focus to the firmware 2D
# grid (assert_menu_focus). This script adds the VISUAL half: it navigates the
# focus off the default card and captures the launcher so a human can confirm the
# focus HIGHLIGHT actually renders on the intended card. It is a candidate only —
# NO golden is promoted and NO mask is added in this phase.
#
# Target: Grapher (id 1). It is one RIGHT from the default Calculation (id 0) and
# sits in row 0, so it is fully on-screen with no scroll — the focus highlight
# (blue border + 1.05x overshoot, MainMenu.cpp initStyles/_styleCardFocused) lands
# on a clearly visible card. Being non-default, the screenshot proves the highlight
# moved away from Calculation.
#
# This script does NOT press ENTER and does NOT launch Grapher: it stays in the
# launcher (MENU) the whole time. The two assert_app Menu bookends prove no app
# opened. The focus animation is driven by the deterministic LVGL tick, so the
# settled frame is a pure function of the frame index (reproducible run-to-run);
# the only across-run volatile region is the StatusBar clock (HH:MM).
#
# Run:
#   program --headless --deterministic --script tests/emulator/scripts/menu_focus_grapher_smoke.numos \
#           --frames 800 --screenshot out/menu_focus_grapher_smoke.ppm --quiet
# Exit codes: 0 ok · 2 script/parse error · 4 assertion failure.

log "menu_focus_grapher_smoke: waiting for splash -> launcher"
wait 200

# Booted to the launcher with the default first card focused.
assert_app Menu
assert_menu_focus Calculation

# Move focus RIGHT once: Calculation (id 0) -> Grapher (id 1).
key right
assert_menu_focus Grapher

# Let the focus overshoot animation settle before capturing (250 ms ~ 16 frames
# at step-ms 16; 120 is a generous, non-fragile margin).
wait 120

# Capture the launcher with Grapher focused. The candidate generator also dumps
# the final frame via --screenshot; this in-script shot proves the command works.
screenshot out/menu_focus_grapher_smoke.ppm
log "menu_focus_grapher_smoke: screenshot captured (Grapher focused)"

# Navigation never left the launcher — no card was activated.
assert_app Menu
log "menu_focus_grapher_smoke: PASS - Grapher focused in launcher, no app launched"
